		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Once you hit 34 exp is easy in here.&nbsp;&nbsp;Just learn to quad kite using your AoE spells.  Lots of open areas and always an abundance of mobs.  This tactic propelled me from 34 to 40 in less than a week.  <br><br>Basicaly use your track and find a few mobs close by.  Prefferably all the same type, all thornys or zerkers, or stoneleers.  You want them all with the same movement rate.  Snare each one.  Run them around till you get them bunched and then cast Lightning strike on them.  You can easily take down 4 mobs with one full row of mana.  Great Exp.<br><br>There is a good guide at eqdruids.com for this.</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Diashan WolfBrother<br>Druid of the 47th Season <br>Drinal</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
