		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>This is a great are for exp. but after you hit lvl 42/43 you will want to head over to Burning Wood and kill hornets .. they are great exp. And all your summoned line spells work wonderful on them. Start out with ash hornets since they are easiest, then go to cinder hornets, other 2 are ember hornets and hardest of them all are the scoriea(sp). At lvl 44 you get your new summoned spell that really does some serious dmg.<br><br>Finding a spot to kill these is easy as well .. as you zone in from Dreadlands veer to your right slightly and you will find a little valley follow this till you hit a path .. make a left at the path and follow to flat land. To the left at the base of the hill is the best area to med. Be careful to change views though so u can see all around while you med.<br><br>Once there just head out straight or to the left and you are sure to find many here, if not just track them .. they arent hard to find. But be careful to always have a gate memmed and stay clear of Gullerbacks since some of these are lvl 50 mobs and have the ability to summon you to them and they hit really hard and have just about 100% magic resist.<br><br>Safe Journeys and good hunting!</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Sowin Masheen<br>65th Storm Warden<br>Mithaniel Marr</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=8><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=8&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 he